                The trust also took initiative to promote ayurveda and medicinal Vedic heritage of India by plantation of various medicinal plants and trees which makes the environment healthier to survive in. Since last two years trust in collaboration with “Arogya Bharti” is advancing this mission which still has a long way to go.
            </p>

        </section>

